---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout title="About | Krishna's Knowledge Journal">

<Header />

<main>

<section>

<h2>About Me</h2>

<img
class="about-photo"
src="/profile.jpg"
alt="Photo of Krishna"
/>

<p>

Thank you for visiting Krishna's Knowledge Journal.

I'm Krishna, and I come from a commerce background with professional experience in a Chartered Accountancy firm. I also invest across different asset classes, which continually deepens my understanding of financial markets.

</p>

</section>

<section>

<h2>Why This Journal Exists</h2>

<div class="card">

<p>

This journal was created because I experienced how difficult it can be to learn finance and economics from fragmented sources.

My objective is to explain every important idea from first principles so that readers understand not only what happens, but also why.

</p>

</div>

</section>

<section>

<h2>Mission</h2>

<div class="card">

<p>

To build a long-term knowledge resource covering Finance, Economics, Indian Banking, Taxation and History through structured research, logical reasoning and clear writing.

</p>

</div>

</section>

</main>

<Footer />

</Layout>